Version 0.2 - March 7, 2009

- lots of internal bug fixes
- SSL support
- API change:  PUT (see doc/api.txt)
- improved volume support
- support multiple server listen addresses
- IPv6 support
- more tests
- API change:  X-Data-Sync header
- Client lib API change: stc_new() args changed
- build on FreeBSD 7.1
- use libevent rather than hand-rolled epoll
- explicitly note we are GPLv2 via COPYING, rather than letting
  autotools copy in the file into the current dir via autogen.sh
- remove SQLite usage, rewrite metadata portion of backend
- optimize file data storage (into sub-dirs on local fs)

Version 0.1 - April 14, 2008

- initial release

